        {"title": "实现性能基线比较器", "description": "编写函数compare_with_baseline(current, baseline)，比较当前性能与基线。\n\ncurrent/baseline: dict {metric: value}\n返回性能变化百分比dict", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def compare_with_baseline(current, baseline):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{resp:200}, {resp:100}\", \"expected\": \"{resp:100.0}\"}]", "solution": "def compare_with_baseline(current, baseline):\n    result = {}\n    for k in current:\n        if k in baseline and baseline[k] > 0:\n            change = (current[k] - baseline[k]) / baseline[k] * 100\n            result[k] = round(change, 2)\n    return result", "hint": "计算各指标的变化百分比"},
        {"title": "实现错误率计算器", "description": "编写函数calculate_error_rate(success, failed)，计算错误率。\n\nerror_rate = failed / (success + failed) * 100", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def calculate_error_rate(success, failed):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"950, 50\", \"expected\": \"5.0\"}]", "solution": "def calculate_error_rate(success, failed):\n    total = success + failed\n    if total == 0: return 0\n    return round(failed / total * 100, 2)", "hint": "注意除零保护"},
        {"title": "实现性能测试场景生成器", "description": "编写函数generate_load_profile(total_users, ramp_up_seconds, hold_seconds)，生成负载模型。\n\n返回阶梯式负载列表[(second, users)]", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def generate_load_profile(total_users, ramp_up_seconds, hold_seconds):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"100, 60, 300\", \"expected\": \"load profile\"}]", "solution": "def generate_load_profile(total_users, ramp_up_seconds, hold_seconds):\n    profile = []\n    step = total_users / (ramp_up_seconds // 10)\n    for t in range(0, ramp_up_seconds, 10):\n        users = min(int(step * (t // 10 + 1)), total_users)\n        profile.append((t, users))\n    for t in range(ramp_up_seconds, ramp_up_seconds + hold_seconds, 10):\n        profile.append((t, total_users))\n    return profile", "hint": "分阶段递增用户数"},
        {"title": "实现吞吐量计算器", "description": "编写函数calculate_throughput(bytes_transferred, duration_seconds)，计算吞吐量。\n\n返回MB/s", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def calculate_throughput(bytes_transferred, duration_seconds):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"1048576, 1\", \"expected\": \"1.0\"}]", "solution": "def calculate_throughput(bytes_transferred, duration_seconds):\n    if duration_seconds == 0: return 0\n    return round(bytes_transferred / duration_seconds / 1048576, 2)", "hint": "1MB = 1048576字节"},
        {"title": "实现SLA验证器", "description": "编写函数check_sla(response_times, max_avg, max_p95)，检查是否满足SLA。\n\nmax_avg: 最大平均响应时间\nmax_p95: 最大95%响应时间", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def check_sla(response_times, max_avg, max_p95):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[100,200,300], 500, 400\", \"expected\": \"passed\"}]", "solution": "def check_sla(response_times, max_avg, max_p95):\n    avg = sum(response_times) / len(response_times)\n    sorted_t = sorted(response_times)\n    p95 = sorted_t[int(len(sorted_t) * 0.95) - 1]\n    if avg > max_avg or p95 > max_p95: return failed\n    return passed", "hint": "计算平均值和95%百分位后比较"},
        {"title": "实现Locust任务类", "description": "编写一个Locust用户类的代码框架，包含登录和浏览商品两个任务。\n\n任务权重: 登录1, 浏览3", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "Locust脚本", "code_template": "from locust import HttpUser, task, between\n\nclass WebsiteUser(HttpUser):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"locust class\", \"expected\": \"valid class\"}]", "solution": "from locust import HttpUser, task, between\nclass WebsiteUser(HttpUser):\n    wait_time = between(1, 3)\n    @task(1)\n    def login(self):\n        self.client.post(\"/login\", {username: test, password: test})\n    @task(3)\n    def browse_products(self):\n        self.client.get(\"/products\")", "hint": "使用@task装饰器设置权重"},
        {"title": "实现性能数据CSV解析器", "description": "编写函数parse_jmeter_csv(filepath)，解析JMeter结果CSV。\n\n返回: dict {avg_time, total_requests, error_rate, throughput}", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "JMeter使用", "code_template": "def parse_jmeter_csv(data_lines):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[line1,line2,line3]\", \"expected\": \"stats dict\"}]", "solution": "def parse_jmeter_csv(data_lines):\n    total = len(data_lines)\n    times = [float(line.split(',')[0]) for line in data_lines]\n    errors = sum(1 for line in data_lines if 'false' in line)\n    return {avg_time: sum(times)/total, total_requests: total, error_rate: errors/total*100, throughput: total/max(times, default=1)}", "hint": "解析CSV行提取时间和状态"},
        {"title": "实现性能瓶颈检测器", "description": "编写函数detect_bottleneck(metrics)，检测性能瓶颈。\n\nmetrics: dict {cpu, memory, disk_io, network}\n阈值: cpu>80%, memory>85%, disk_io>70%, network>90%\n返回瓶颈指标列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "code_template": "def detect_bottleneck(metrics):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{cpu:90,memory:50,disk_io:30,network:20}\", \"expected\": \"[cpu]\"}]", "solution": "def detect_bottleneck(metrics):\n    thresholds = {cpu: 80, memory: 85, disk_io: 70, network: 90}\n    return [k for k, v in metrics.items() if v > thresholds.get(k, 100)]", "hint": "遍历指标与阈值比较"},
        {"title": "实现阶梯负载生成器", "description": "编写函数step_load_generator(users_per_step, step_duration, max_steps)，生成阶梯负载。\n\n返回每步的用户数列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def step_load_generator(users_per_step, step_duration, max_steps):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"10, 60, 5\", \"expected\": \"[10,20,30,40,50]\"}]", "solution": "def step_load_generator(users_per_step, step_duration, max_steps):\n    return [users_per_step * (i + 1) for i in range(max_steps)]", "hint": "每步递增users_per_step"},
        {"title": "实现Apdex计算器", "description": "编写函数calculate_apdex(satisfied, tolerating, total)，计算Apdex分数。\n\nApdex = (satisfied + tolerating/2) / total\n返回分数和等级", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def calculate_apdex(satisfied, tolerating, total):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"80, 15, 100\", \"expected\": \"(0.875, Good)\"}]", "solution": "def calculate_apdex(satisfied, tolerating, total):\n    if total == 0: return (0, None)\n    score = (satisfied + tolerating / 2) / total\n    if score >= 0.94: level = Excellent\n    elif score >= 0.85: level = Good\n    elif score >= 0.7: level = Fair\n    elif score >= 0.5: level = Poor\n    else: level = Unacceptable\n    return (round(score, 3), level)", "hint": "Apdex分数范围决定等级"},
        {"title": "实现并发连接池模拟器", "description": "编写函数simulate_connection_pool(pool_size, request_count)，模拟连接池。\n\n返回排队等待的最大请求数", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def simulate_connection_pool(pool_size, request_count):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"5, 10\", \"expected\": \"5\"}]", "solution": "def simulate_connection_pool(pool_size, request_count):\n    if request_count <= pool_size: return 0\n    return request_count - pool_size", "hint": "超出池大小的请求需要排队"},
        {"title": "实现性能趋势分析器", "description": "编写函数analyze_trend(weekly_data)，分析性能趋势。\n\nweekly_data: list of {week, avg_response_time}\n返回: improving/stable/degrading", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "code_template": "def analyze_trend(weekly_data):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[{week:1,time:100},{week:2,time:150}]\", \"expected\": \"degrading\"}]", "solution": "def analyze_trend(weekly_data):\n    times = [d[avg_response_time] for d in weekly_data]\n    if len(times) < 3: return stable\n    recent = times[-3:]\n    if all(recent[i] > recent[i-1] for i in range(1, len(recent))): return degrading\n    if all(recent[i] < recent[i-1] for i in range(1, len(recent))): return improving\n    return stable", "hint": "比较最近几周的趋势"},
        {"title": "实现性能测试数据去重", "description": "编写函数deduplicate_requests(requests)，去除重复请求。\n\nrequests: list of {url, method, timestamp}\n返回去重后的列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def deduplicate_requests(requests):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[{url:/a,method:GET},{url:/a,method:GET}]\", \"expected\": \"[{url:/a,method:GET}]\"}]", "solution": "def deduplicate_requests(requests):\n    seen = set()\n    result = []\n    for r in requests:\n        key = (r[url], r[method])\n        if key not in seen:\n            seen.add(key)\n            result.append(r)\n    return result", "hint": "用集合记录已见请求"},
        {"title": "实现性能阈值检查器", "description": "编写函数check_thresholds(metrics, thresholds)，检查性能指标是否超阈值。\n\n返回超阈值的指标列表及超标百分比", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def check_thresholds(metrics, thresholds):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{resp:500}, {resp:300}\", \"expected\": \"[{metric:resp,excess:66.7}]\"}]", "solution": "def check_thresholds(metrics, thresholds):\n    violations = []\n    for k, v in metrics.items():\n        if k in thresholds and v > thresholds[k]:\n            excess = (v - thresholds[k]) / thresholds[k] * 100\n            violations.append({metric: k, excess: round(excess, 1)})\n    return violations", "hint": "遍历比较并计算超标百分比"},
        {"title": "实现性能测试脚本执行器", "description": "编写函数run_performance_test(config)，执行性能测试。\n\nconfig: {url, users, duration}\n返回模拟的测试结果", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def run_performance_test(config):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{url:http://test,users:10,duration:60}\", \"expected\": \"test result\"}]", "solution": "def run_performance_test(config):\n    import random\n    total_requests = config[users] * config[duration]\n    avg_time = random.randint(50, 500)\n    error_rate = random.uniform(0, 5)\n    return {total_requests: total_requests, avg_response_time: avg_time, error_rate: round(error_rate, 2), tps: round(total_requests / config[duration], 2)}", "hint": "模拟生成性能测试结果"},
        {"title": "实现资源使用率汇总", "description": "编写函数summarize_resource_usage(samples)，汇总资源使用情况。\n\nsamples: list of {cpu, memory, disk}\n返回各指标的平均值、最大值", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "code_template": "def summarize_resource_usage(samples):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"[{cpu:50,memory:60},{cpu:70,memory:80}]\", \"expected\": \"avg cpu:60, max cpu:70\"}]", "solution": "def summarize_resource_usage(samples):\n    result = {}\n    for key in samples[0]:\n        values = [s[key] for s in samples]\n        result[key] = {avg: sum(values)/len(values), max: max(values)}\n    return result", "hint": "遍历各指标计算统计值"},
        {"title": "实现性能回归检测", "description": "编写函数detect_regression(current, previous, threshold)，检测性能回归。\n\nthreshold: 回归阈值百分比\n返回回归的指标列表", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "code_template": "def detect_regression(current, previous, threshold):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{resp:300}, {resp:100}, 50\", \"expected\": \"[resp]\"}]", "solution": "def detect_regression(current, previous, threshold):\n    regressions = []\n    for k in current:\n        if k in previous and previous[k] > 0:\n            change = (current[k] - previous[k]) / previous[k] * 100\n            if change > threshold:\n                regressions.append(k)\n    return regressions", "hint": "计算变化百分比并比较阈值"},
        {"title": "实现性能测试摘要生成", "description": "编写函数generate_perf_summary(results)，生成性能测试摘要。\n\nresults: dict {total_req, avg_resp, error_rate, tps}\n返回格式化摘要字符串", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def generate_perf_summary(results):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"{total:1000,avg:200,error:2.5,tps:50}\", \"expected\": \"summary string\"}]", "solution": "def generate_perf_summary(results):\n    return f\"Total:{results[total_req]}, AvgResp:{results[avg_resp]}ms, ErrorRate:{results[error_rate]}%, TPS:{results[tps]}\"", "hint": "格式化各指标"},
        {"title": "实现性能容量预测器", "description": "编写函数predict_capacity(current_tps, growth_rate, months)，预测系统容量。\n\n预测months月后的TPS需求", "instructions": "请编写代码实现以下功能", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "code_template": "def predict_capacity(current_tps, growth_rate, months):\n    pass", "test_cases": "[{\"input\": \"100, 0.1, 6\", \"expected\": \"177.2\"}]", "solution": "def predict_capacity(current_tps, growth_rate, months):\n    return round(current_tps * (1 + growth_rate) ** months, 1)", "hint": "使用复利增长公式"},

        # ==================== 简答题 (25题) ====================
        {"title": "性能测试类型对比", "description": "对比负载测试、压力测试、稳定性测试和容量测试的区别和适用场景。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "easy", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "solution": "负载测试: 验证正常预期负载下的系统表现。压力测试: 找到系统极限和崩溃点。稳定性测试: 长时间运行验证系统稳定性。容量测试: 确定系统能处理的最大数据量。适用场景: 负载测试用于性能验收，压力测试用于了解系统极限，稳定性测试用于上线前验证，容量测试用于规划扩展。"},
        {"title": "性能测试指标体系", "description": "描述Web应用性能测试的核心指标体系。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "solution": "核心指标: 1)响应时间: 平均/P90/P95/P99 2)吞吐量: TPS/QPS 3)并发用户数 4)错误率 5)资源使用率: CPU/内存/磁盘IO/网络 6)Apdex分数。监控维度: 前端(页面加载时间)、应用层(接口响应)、服务器(资源使用)、数据库(查询性能)。"},
        {"title": "性能瓶颈分析方法", "description": "描述如何进行系统性能瓶颈分析。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "solution": "分析方法: 1)监控资源使用率(CPU/内存/IO/网络) 2)分析慢查询日志 3)使用APM工具追踪请求链路 4)代码profiling定位热点 5)数据库执行计划分析 6)网络抓包分析 7)逐步增加负载找到拐点。常见瓶颈: 数据库查询、外部API调用、内存泄漏、线程阻塞、网络延迟。"},
        {"title": "JMeter测试计划设计", "description": "描述如何设计一个完整的JMeter性能测试计划。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "JMeter使用", "solution": "设计步骤: 1)创建线程组(设置并发数和Ramp-Up) 2)添加配置元件(HTTP头管理器、CSV参数化) 3)添加取样器(HTTP请求) 4)添加断言(响应断言) 5)添加监听器(聚合报告、图形结果) 6)设置定时器(模拟Think Time) 7)配置分布式压测。注意: 参数化、关联、检查点。"},
        {"title": "Locust框架优势", "description": "描述Locust性能测试框架的优势和适用场景。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "Locust脚本", "solution": "优势: 1)Python编写脚本，学习成本低 2)支持分布式 3)Web UI实时查看结果 4)代码驱动灵活 5)支持自定义负载模型。适用场景: API性能测试、复杂业务场景模拟、需要编程灵活性的场景。与JMeter对比: Locust更灵活但功能较少，适合有编程能力的团队。"},
        {"title": "性能测试环境准备", "description": "描述性能测试环境的准备要点。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "solution": "准备要点: 1)环境配置与生产环境尽量一致 2)独立的测试环境避免干扰 3)测试数据准备(接近生产数据量) 4)数据库预置数据 5)环境健康检查 6)网络环境确认 7)监控工具部署 8)清理历史数据。注意: 不要在开发环境做性能测试。"},
        {"title": "性能测试数据分析", "description": "如何分析性能测试结果数据？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "solution": "分析方法: 1)响应时间趋势图(是否有增长趋势) 2)TPS曲线(找到最大吞吐量) 3)错误率变化(什么时候开始出错) 4)资源使用率关联分析 5)与基线对比 6)百分位数分析(P90/P95/P99) 7)各接口分别分析 8)找出拐点(性能急剧下降的点)。工具: Grafana、Excel、Python数据分析。"},
        {"title": "性能调优策略", "description": "描述常见的性能调优策略和方法。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "solution": "调优策略: 1)数据库优化(索引、查询优化、缓存) 2)代码优化(算法、减少IO) 3)缓存策略(Redis、CDN) 4)异步处理(消息队列) 5)连接池配置 6)负载均衡 7)代码并发优化 8)资源扩容。原则: 先测量再优化，聚焦最大瓶颈，量化优化效果。"},
        {"title": "分布式压测架构", "description": "描述分布式性能测试的架构设计。", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "分布式压测", "solution": "架构: 1)Master节点: 控制测试执行、收集结果 2)Slave节点: 执行实际请求 3)协调机制: 同步启动、负载分配 4)结果汇总: 集中收集和分析。设计要点: Slave节点资源充足、网络带宽足够、避免Slave本身成为瓶颈、监控Slave节点状态。JMeter和Locust都支持分布式。"},
        {"title": "性能测试中的数据准备", "description": "性能测试数据准备有哪些方法和注意事项？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "solution": "方法: 1)从生产环境脱敏复制 2)脚本批量生成 3)使用Faker库 4)数据库直接导入。注意事项: 数据量要接近生产、数据分布要合理、测试前清理脏数据、使用唯一数据避免冲突、敏感数据脱敏、数据准备脚本版本化管理。"},
        {"title": "Web前端性能测试", "description": "Web前端性能测试关注哪些指标？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能指标", "solution": "前端指标: 1)首屏时间(FCP) 2)可交互时间(TTI) 3)页面加载时间 4)资源加载瀑布图 5)JS执行时间 6)DOM节点数 7)请求数和资源大小 8)缓存命中率。工具: Lighthouse、WebPageTest、Chrome DevTools。优化: 减少请求、压缩资源、CDN、懒加载。"},
        {"title": "数据库性能测试", "description": "如何进行数据库性能测试？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能瓶颈分析", "solution": "测试内容: 1)慢查询分析和优化 2)索引效果验证 3)并发读写测试 4)连接池配置 5)事务隔离级别测试 6)大数据量查询性能 7)存储过程性能 8)主从复制延迟。工具: sysbench、mysqlslap、EXPLAIN分析。关注: 查询响应时间、QPS、锁等待。"},
        {"title": "性能测试自动化", "description": "如何将性能测试集成到CI/CD流程？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "hard", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "solution": "集成方式: 1)在CI中运行轻量级性能测试 2)设置性能阈值作为质量门禁 3)使用命令行工具(JMeter CLI、Locust) 4)自动生成报告 5)与基线对比检测回归 6)定时执行全面性能测试 7)异常告警。注意: CI中的性能测试应轻量化，全面测试定期执行。"},
        {"title": "性能测试中的思考时间", "description": "性能测试中如何合理设置思考时间？", "instructions": "请详细回答以下问题", "exercise_type": "text", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "性能测试", "knowledge_point": "性能测试概念", "solution": "思考时间模拟用户操作间隔。设置方法: 1)分析真实用户行为日志 2)使用固定值或随机范围 3)根据测试目标调整(压力测试可减少) 4)保持与真实场景一致。影响: 思考时间越长，并发压力越小; 可设为0测试系统极限。最佳实践: 使用随机范围模拟真实行为。"},
